{{for|the scientific concepts|Multiverse|Many-worlds interpretation}}

{{Multiple issues|
{{overly detailed|date=August 2010}}
{{Refimprove|date=July 2011}}
{{original research|date=July 2011}}
{{essay-like|date=July 2011}}
{{Example farm|date=October 2015}}
